developer_response.body:
Hello!
Thank you for letting me know! I will look into it and this days an update will solve this issues.
Thank you! 

Update:
A new update is available, it should fix the machines and food items. 
Thank you for contacting me and never hesitate to tell me bout whatever issue or idea, I am here at any time!

V: 1.0.9: 
* NEW! OUTSIDE TERRACE - (nou you can extend the shop, more customers in the coffee shop at the same time); 
* New AI mechanics; 
* Coffee Machines now can't be moved; 
* Food-boxes added; 
* Added 1 breakable item(experimental for further updates - the vase in the office room); 
* Other bugs fixed; 

Enjoy !
